  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      National, prospective, multicentre observational study designed for eligible patients treated
      with Inflectra.

      Its objectives are to describe under real conditions of use, the profile of patients treated
      with Inflectra and the response to treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
